data.description: Experience the essence of modern farmhouse living with this meticulously rebuilt haven in Covington. Every detail carefully crafted, from the high-end gourmet kitchen with its sprawling island to the seamless flow of the open concept layout, perfect for entertaining or simply savoring everyday moments. Situated near parks and shopping, enjoy the serenity of a vast flat lot, nearly 1/3 acre in size, complete with a fenced yard and convenient vehicle charging station for eco-conscious living. Step inside to discover the timeless allure of original hardwood floors, imbued with character that only ages can bring. Admire the charm of original fireplaces, now ornamental features adding a touch of history to the contemporary ambiance. Retreat to the screened porch, offering a tranquil space to unwind and relish the outdoors in comfort or enjoy the gas fireplace in the family room during the chilly months. The allure continues indoors with lofty 10-foot ceilings, enhancing the sense of spaciousness and airiness throughout. Revel in the abundance of natural light that floods the kitchen and living areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere year-round. Explore the outdoors even further as this home is located in a golf cart district, where residents are legally permitted to enjoy leisurely rides to the city just one mile away. Whether entertaining or enjoying peaceful solitude, this farmhouse exudes luxury and charm in equal measure, offering a unique blend of modern comforts and timeless elegance.
